<OUTPUT_TEXT>
"Good morning, Maplewood Medical Clinic, this is your Medical Secretary. How may I assist you today?"
[Pause, simulating listening to the caller's request]
"I understand you're calling to schedule a follow-up appointment. For all appointment bookings, I will connect you directly with our scheduling coordinator. Please hold while I transfer your call."
[Brief pause, simulating transfer]
"You are now being connected to the scheduling department."
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
